{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"區塊語法","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Control_flow_and_error_handling","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"區塊語法","title":"區塊語法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>區塊語法用於把語句群組化。區塊的範圍是由一對大括號所界定︰</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">{\n   statement_1\n   statement_2\n   .\n   .\n   .\n   statement_n\n}\n</pre>\n<p><strong>範例</strong><br> 區塊語法通常和流程控制語法（例如 <code>if</code>、<code>for</code>、<code>while</code>）一併使用。</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">while (x &lt; 10) {\n   x++;\n}\n</pre>\n<p>此處，<code>{ x++; }</code> 就是區塊語法。</p>\n<p><strong>重要</strong>: JavaScript <strong>並沒有</strong> 區塊作用域。區塊裡的變數其作用域相當於函數或 Script，對變數的設定會一直持續到區塊本身之外。換言之，區塊語法並沒有作用域。儘管“單獨”的區塊仍是有效的句法，你也不會想要在 JavaScript 中使用單獨的區塊，因為這樣做並不會產生任何你所期待的機能，譬如說如果你期待類似 C 或 Java 而這樣做的話。例如︰</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">var x = 1;\n{\n   var x = 2;\n}\nalert(x); // 輸出 2\n</pre>\n<p>這樣會輸出 2，因為在區塊之內的 <code>var x</code> 語法，其作用域如同沒有區塊的 <code>var x</code> 語法。而在 C 或 Java 中，同樣的代碼將會輸出 1。</p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\"> <p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/正規表達式的運用/正規表達式的範例\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/條件語法\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"區塊語法用於把語句群組化。區塊的範圍是由一對大括號所界定︰","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Control flow and error handling","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/control_flow_and_error_handling","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/control_flow_and_error_handling/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Control_flow_and_error_handling","title":"區塊語法"}],"pageTitle":"區塊語法 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}